api_list.name: Get Tripura Districts
api_list.description: This endpoint will return Tripura District's petrol price
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://daily-petrol-price-in-india.p.rapidapi.com/tripura"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "daily-petrol-price-in-india.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
